Description: Rest on the Flight into Egypt; night scene with St Joseph sitting in the centre, his head resting on his left hand and a walking stick in his right hand, the Virgin and the Christ Child at right, a lantern hanging from a tree at left, a horse in the lower left corner. 1642 Etching
Producer name: Formerly attributed to: Johannes van Noordt IV (van der Kellen)
